item.title: About Us
item.description: Iowa is perhaps the only state in the U.S. that has a sustained Community Visioning   program. Their mission… Iowa’s Community Visioning: We help small Iowa communities bridge the gap between the demand and availability of design resources needed to improve transportation systems. Tama-Toledo Community Visioning Upon completion of our 2021 “program year” with Community Visioning   , it was clear to the Tama and Toledo CV steering committees that we need to work together to address the needs of our broader Tama-Toledo community.
